    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>What a fabulous post, Molly!  I absolutely LOVE your blog and cannot wait to buy your book.</></>I haven&#8217;t checked out Shauna&#8217;s blog yet, but now I think I must&#8230;</></>I tried your Banana Bread with Chocolate and Cinnamon Sugar a few weeks ago and thought it was amazing.  Would it be acceptable if I posted the recipe on my blog?  Pretty please?  A bread this good deserves to be shared by many!  If I post it, I will of course give credit where credit is due.</></>Keep on cookin&#8217; and writin&#8217;!</>Rosiecat</p>
