    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>It has been cold &#038; raining/snowing(!) here the last few days. I made this wonderful recipe again and it was perfect for the weather.</></>I find eating it with a spoon as well as knife and fork is best &#8211; a spoon ensures the scrumptious sauce, compote &#038; brat are present in every bite. I find for two that the compote is enough for two meals.</></>Thanks Molly!</>c2c</>from your honeymoon Island</p>
